org.deeplearning4j.ui.storage

Class InMemoryStatsStorage

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.deeplearning4j.ui.storage.BaseCollectionStatsStorage
      • org.deeplearning4j.ui.storage.InMemoryStatsStorage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.deeplearning4j.api.storage.StatsStorage, org.deeplearning4j.api.storage.StatsStorageRouter

    public class InMemoryStatsStorage
extends BaseCollectionStatsStorage
    A StatsStorage implementation that stores all data in memory. If persistence is required for the UI information, use FileStatsStorage or MapDBStatsStorage.
    Internally, this implementation uses MapDBStatsStorage
